      <title>拜登将赦免因同性恋而被定罪的美国军人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/us-veterans-convicted-due-to-sexual-orientation-to-get-biden-pardon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将发表公告，对在冷战时期清洗同性恋者行动中被定罪的美国军人给予大规模赦免，从而扭转数十年来迫使约 10 万人退役的歧视政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/us-veterans-convicted-due-to-sexual-orientation-to-get-biden-pardon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥反对派陷入混乱，奥夫拉多尔推动改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/battered-mexico-opposition-in-disarray-as-amlo-pushes-for-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥反对派未能阻止安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔的“更多党”继续担任总统，并在本月初的选举中取得巨大胜利。现在，这个饱受打击、脆弱的联盟面临着更大的挑战：如何阻止他在卸任前批准备受争议的全面宪法改革计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/battered-mexico-opposition-in-disarray-as-amlo-pushes-for-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国工业界担心港口罢工，敦促拜登重启谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/us-industries-fearing-a-port-strike-urge-biden-to-revive-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数十个美国行业协会敦促白宫帮助重启美国东部和墨西哥湾沿岸码头工人与港口运营商之间陷入僵局的谈判，并表示在全球供应链已经紧张的情况下，罢工是经济最不需要的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/us-industries-fearing-a-port-strike-urge-biden-to-revive-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:46:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员等待内阁公告，南非兰特走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/south-african-rand-weakens-as-traders-await-cabinet-announcement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非兰特连续第三天走弱，交易员等待内阁任命消息，近一个月前选举导致总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 领导的政党失去议会多数席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/south-african-rand-weakens-as-traders-await-cabinet-announcement</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约批准荷兰领导人吕特接替斯托尔滕贝格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/naio-approves-dutch-prime-minister-rutte-to-succeed-stoltenberg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约在一份声明中表示，荷兰首相马克·吕特将接替今年晚些时候卸任的延斯·斯托尔滕贝格，成为下一任北约秘书长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/naio-approves-dutch-prime-minister-rutte-to-succeed-stoltenberg</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:30:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克执政党认为紧缩政策仍是赢得选举的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/austerity-is-still-an-election-winner-czech-ruling-party-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国主要执政党在议会选举前一年进行了一次政治赌博，通过推进紧缩措施，到目前为止，这些措施已增强了民粹主义反对派的支持率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/austerity-is-still-an-election-winner-czech-ruling-party-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:02:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国严厉打击美化恐怖主义行为的外国人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/germany-cracks-down-on-foreigners-who-glorify-terrorist-acts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国执政联盟正寻求通过最新立法严厉打击美化杀害以色列平民或类似恐怖行为的外国人，以便将他们驱逐出境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/germany-cracks-down-on-foreigners-who-glorify-terrorist-acts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 07:53:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>甘地担任印度议会反对党领袖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/rahul-gandhi-becomes-leader-of-opposition-in-india-s-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度反对派正准备在议会中发挥更大作用，提名拉胡尔·甘地担任重要职位，并派出自己的候选人参加下议院议长竞选，这是一次罕见的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/rahul-gandhi-becomes-leader-of-opposition-in-india-s-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:51:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默的目标是英国难以达到的 2.5% 的增长率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-labour-to-seek-economic-growth-of-at-least-2-5-starmer-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民意调查显示，基尔·斯塔默有望成为英国下一任首相，他表示，如果工党赢得大选，将寻求至少 2.5% 的年增长率 - 但经济学家认为这一增长率是不现实的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-labour-to-seek-economic-growth-of-at-least-2-5-starmer-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚总统部署军队制止“叛国”抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-president-deploys-military-to-halt-treasonous-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托严厉谴责全国范围内的反政府抗议活动，称其为“叛国行为”，并部署军队结束骚乱。抗议活动遭到警方的残酷镇压，造成至少 17 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-president-deploys-military-to-halt-treasonous-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
